how to deploy an app to netlify :-
create an angular app using cli
add an "_redirects" file in src with contents:-
/*    /index.html    200

add "src/_redirects" in myproject.architect.build.options.asset array in angular.json

push the code to github 
buiuld configuration netlify
        Repository                  github.com/ankush0024/movieMadness
        Base directory                      Not set
         Build command                   ng build --prod --aot
       Publish directory            dist/movieMadness
       Deploy log visibility             Logs are public
       Builds                         Active